# wexample-filestate-python

Helpers for Python.

Version: 0.0.40

## Requirements

- Python >=3.10

## Dependencies

- autoflake
- black
- flynt
- isort
- networkx
- packaging
- pydantic>=2,<3
- python-dotenv
- pyupgrade
- tomlkit
- wexample-filestate-git==0.0.38

## Installation

```bash
pip install wexample-filestate-python
```

## Links

- Homepage: https://github.com/wexample/python-filestate-python
